asset.title: 2011, 2012, 2013 and 2014 Ford Mustang GT 5.0L Air Intake Installation
asset.description:
See how easy it is to add more performance to the 2011, 2012, 2013 and 2014 Ford Mustang GT with the 5.0L engine.

http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=69-3527TP

K&N 69-3527TP air intake modification showed an estimated gain of 19.5 horsepower at 5100 RPM when tested on the K&N dynamometer. 

K&N 69-3527TP fits the following: 
2014 FORD MUSTANG GT 5.0L V8 
2013 FORD MUSTANG GT 5.0L V8 
2012 FORD MUSTANG GT 5.0L V8 
2011 FORD MUSTANG GT 5.0L V8
 
Go to http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=69-3527TP for an up to date application list.

To search for your own vehicle's corresponding cold air intake and air filter visit
http://www.KNfilters.com
